         <abstract id="aspace_17798693ab0c80dc48a6f09417bedb7f">The collection consists of formal portraits of various Yale presidents up to and including Kingman Brewster. Also in the collection are photographs of various presidents' homes. The portraits were used by Reuben Holden for his 1968 book Profiles and Portraits of Yale University Presidents.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname identifier="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/no95020771"
                      source="naf">
               <part>Holden, Reuben A. (Reuben Andrus), 1918-</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_eaed50f5185b9001bc730302837298af">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 48-A (YRG 48-A), Yale pictorial records and collections.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_201f645d1eaa6660558022938a3ea8bc">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Reuben A. Holden Photographs Used in the Publication "Profiles and Portraits of Yale Univerity Presidents" (RU 652). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_1de0202ebfb788df11476be140d77b7f">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_b36399641a4c33aa07b95b8c994687b4">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged chronologically by tenure.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_a7edabb8aa07a7a0eadcedbe9bdc5adc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of formal portraits of various Yale presidents up to and including Kingman Brewster. Also in the collection are photographs of various presidents' homes. The portraits were used by Reuben Holden for his 1968 book Profiles and Portraits of Yale University Presidents.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
